title: "It's not over yet": Republican Saccone on too-close-to-call Pennsylvania race
text:
"It's not over yet": Republican Saccone on too-close-to-call Pennsylvania race 8:00am EDT - 00:32 
Conservative Republican candidate Rick Saccone tells his supporters the congressional race is not over yet and he's ''going to fight all the way to the end.'' Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
